        <div class="related-tag">Paper</div>
        <h3>The retrieval precision paper</h3>
        <p>Formal treatment of belief typing, BM25 retrieval, and scope isolation as memory system requirements.</p>
        <span class="related-link">Read on arXiv →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

